ABOUT THIS PROJECT:

This advanced recommendation system implements a sophisticated two-stage 
architecture for content discovery and ranking:

1. Retrieval Stage: Efficiently narrows down millions of candidates using 
   a two-tower neural architecture with approximate nearest neighbor search.

2. Ranking Stage: Scores and orders retrieved candidates using a transformer 
   model that predicts multiple engagement types.

The system combines in-network content (from followed accounts) with 
out-of-network content (discovered through ML-based retrieval) to provide 
personalized recommendations.

